### TC10 - Wrong content type (415/400 depending converter)
POST {{baseUrl}}/usage/{{serial}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: text/plain

just-text

> {%
client.test("TC10 - Status is 415 or 400", function() {
  client.assert(response.status === 415 || response.status === 400);
});
%}


